quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,Мре tokelaki moto na mabele ya kokawuka oyo ezwami na mabele ya muselu
  15,27,Mpe tokelaki ba djini liboso na moto ya molunge makasi
  15,28,"Mpe tango Nkolo wayo alobaki na ba anzelu ete: Ya soló nalingi kokela moto na mabele ya kokawuka oyo ezwami na mabele ya muselu"
  15,29,"Mpe tango nakosilisa kobongisa ye na lolenge ya kitoko mpe na fuli okati naye, pema nangai bofukamela ye na botosi"
  15,30,Mpe ba anzelu banso bafukamaki
  15,31,"Longola sé lusufele (ibilisa), aboyaka kogumbama elongo na bagumbami"
  15,32,"Na yango (Allah) alobaki: Oh lusufele! Mpona nini ozuami o motango mwa bagumbami te"
  15,33,"Alobi: Nazali te mpona kogumbamela moto oyo okeli ye kowuta na mabele ya kokawuka oyo ezwami na mabele ya muselu"
  15,34,"Mpe (Allah) alobi: Bima wana (na lola) mpo ozali na botutu"
  15,35,Mpe okozala na botutu kino mokolo mwa suka
  15,36,"Alobi: Oh Nkolo wa ngai! Pesa ngai mwa tango kino mokolo mwa bosekwisami"
  15,37,"Мре (Allah) alobaki naye ete: Ya soló, ozali kati ya bazelisami"
  15,38,Kino mokolo ya ngonga eye eyebani
  15,39,"Alobi: Oh Nkolo wa ngai! Pamba te mpo omemi ngai na libungi, mpe na kobongisela bango mokili mpe nakobungisa bango banso"
  15,40,Longola sé bawumbu nayo baye osilaki коропа
  15,41,"(Allah) alobi: Oyo nde nzela ya bokambami epai na ngai"
  15,42,"Ya solo, bawumbu ba ngai ozali na bokonzi likolo na bango te longola sé baye bakolanda yo nakati ya babungi"
  15,43,"Mpe ya soló, lifelo ekozala esika na bango banso"
  15,44,"Ezali na bikuke sambo тропа kokota, mpe bikuke binso biyebani na bato ba yango"